    58→### Parse a TOML string<a name="parse-a-toml-string"></a>
    59→
    60→```python
    61→import tomli
    62→
    63→toml_str = """
    64→[[players]]
    65→name = "Lehtinen"
    66→number = 26
    67→
    68→[[players]]
    69→name = "Numminen"
    70→number = 27
    71→"""
    72→
    73→toml_dict = tomli.loads(toml_str)
    74→assert toml_dict == {
    75→    "players": [{"name": "Lehtinen", "number": 26}, {"name": "Numminen", "number": 27}]
    76→}
    77→```
